snippet.title: Episode 1 Adding Fractions
snippet.description:
TeacherTube User: Professormccomb

TeacherTube URL: http://www.teachertube.com/viewVideo.php?video_id=267745

This is a math video lesson to help you with new math, math tricks, and or simple math questions you may have. 

Travel to ParallelaLand and learn how to add fractions with the help of Professor McComb and her students Adam Diffy Q Delta Polly Denom amp Ator. Featuring special guest star N.O.I.D. Number One in Disguise. Youll have your problems unFOILed.
